<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>44-951.18</num>
  <heading>Authority of the Chief Financial Officer.</heading>
  <text>The Chief Financial Officer of the District of Columbia shall exercise authority over the Corporation consistent with §§ <cite path="§1-204.24a">1-204.24a</cite> through <cite path="§1-204.24f">1-204.24f</cite>.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation doc="D.C. Law 19-21" type="History" path="§5129">Sept. 14, 2011, D.C. Law 19-21, § 5129, 58 DCR 6226</annotation>
    <annotation doc="D.C. Law 19-171" type="History">Sept. 26, 2012, D.C. Law 19-171, § 107, 59 DCR 6190</annotation>
    <annotation type="Effect of Amendments">The 2012 amendment by <cite doc="D.C. Law 19-171">D.C. Law 19-171</cite> substituted “§§ <cite path="§1-204.24a">1-204.24a</cite> through <cite path="§1-204.24f">1-204.24f</cite>” for “§§ <cite path="§1-204.24a">1-204.24a</cite>, <cite path="§1-204.24b">1-204.24b</cite>, and <cite path="§1-204.24c">1-204.24c</cite>.”</annotation>
  </annotations>
